Description:
   Gap Probe is the first application of Gap Intuition: before a gap in an
   opponent's defense can be exploited, it must be found. This technique is
   assessment. The Cipher delivers a testing strike that searches for
   structural fault — a probe rather than a committed blow. At level 1 the
   Cipher cannot yet exploit what they find, but the strike itself carries
   force and begins building their read of the target.

   Damage is calculated from pseudo-level and Strength (same as Warden
   melee skills). The Cipher's deeper combat skills — backstab, circle,
   mark target — build on the gap assessment this technique initiates.

   Syntax: gap probe <target>
   Requires POS_FIGHTING. Can be practiced to improve hit rate.
